{"tid":1758887,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"回瑞超踢波係假象 伊巴入股哈馬比做老闆先真","createTime":"2019-11-27T10:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T03:20:28.000Z","uid":12360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"72a6556821cf606279f3ecb76e138f0157bcae29","tid":1758887,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T10:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191127/large/1574846831_5952.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191127%2Flarge%2F1574846831_5952.jpg&h=fb1fc765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瑞典神鋒伊巴謙莫域日前在Instagram上載一段短片，內容是一件哈馬比球衣背後印了他的名字，一度令人懷疑他已決定重返瑞超加盟這間球會，但後經證實原來是他買入這間球會的股份，成為其中一位班主。<br />\n<br />\n哈馬比周三在官網宣佈，伊巴已成為他們其中一位股東，原因是原本持該球會股份的AEG集團（Anschutz Entertainment Group），將自己手上一半的股份售予伊巴，三方日前已在洛杉磯洽談，也已落實。<br />\n<br />\nAEG本身也是伊巴前球會洛杉磯銀河的股東之一，代表伊巴與銀河之間的關係仍密切。伊巴透過球會官網表示：「哈馬比是一間偉大的球會，擁有很多熱情的球迷，也在斯德哥爾摩及瑞典廣受尊重。我一直都很喜歡這間球會，也被他們近年在場內場外所做的事情吸引住，能夠加入這裏和幫助球會發展，既刺激又有趣。」<br />\n<br />\n今月已與銀河約滿的伊巴，仍未確定下一站去向。這位前鋒有傳會重返意甲，已先後與前東家AC米蘭、拿玻里及博洛尼亞扯上關係，而當摩連奴接掌熱刺後，也有指這間倫敦球會有意向他招手，但摩佬及後親自澄清他的球隊不需要伊巴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191127/4E2TMOXJQ4DUJWNXZ2YBVENYRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191127%2F4E2TMOXJQ4DUJWNXZ2YBVENYRQ%2F&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRH88up93QrsUiEJqOxYGoBw%3D&h=4effb960\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191127%2F4E2TMOXJQ4DUJWNXZ2YBVENYRQ%2F&h=d38eb9c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191127/4E2TMOXJQ4DUJWNXZ2YBVENYRQ/</a><br />\n扮撚晒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cb1d18eba26f085a031b530a95cd8ec768d973","tid":1758887,"uid":144739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"但摩佬及後親自澄清他的球隊不需要伊巴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebab32b6c63d7c22f0d27c844d2b236c0fad3968","tid":1758887,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:47:37.000Z","msg":"我係左膠頓斯十年球迷，要反伊巴比了"},{"pid":"5fd6fddf3e59622252461c9e8580cced75dff845","tid":1758887,"uid":25758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:48:33.000Z","msg":"買親哈馬比都贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0bed6022a31f7db98c28ec2b70209c1464c0b5","tid":1758887,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:52:10.000Z","msg":"又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a89afd4facfc107face4f4e83fc2a1ad8ceaada","tid":1758887,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1cb1d18eba26f085a031b530a95cd8ec768d973","tid":1758887,"uid":144739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"但摩佬及後親自澄清他的球隊不需要伊巴。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:56:38.000Z","msg":"廢老冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea1353fe501c9b4f549c4c14a47872807d1ec95","tid":1758887,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T12:56:58.000Z","msg":"**** 眾籌 ****<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鍾庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣 話比全世界聽：我地今鋪無輸的念頭<br />\n<br />\n(由於中大民調欠缺資金做今次反送中民調，我們的眾籌會同時加入新項目，籌到的款項亦會用作資助中大民調)<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家80%, 仲差少少</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持<br />\n<br />\n第六期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1745339/page/1</a> <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span>